sub_title: Enterprise Service Manager at Siemens Healthineers
summary:
Pragmatic and fair Program Manager, Business Development Manager, Service and Support Manager that enjoys building relationships and improve processes together with customers and colleagues. I thrive in continuously changing international environments with goals including increased revenue and satisfied customers and employees. Passionate about helping people excel at what they do, embrace change and I break down barriers with empathy and listening skills. Love to contribute with my knowledge to make a significant difference in an organization.  Problems are great opportunities and lifelong learning is my motto.

Over 20 years of work experience in international companies working with People Management, Sales in IT and Medical Equipment (Diagnostics, Research, Life Science), Service management, Marketing, Account Management, Supply Chain, Operations and Program management, Tender negotiations and management, Contract management, Project sales experience, Strategy development, Innovation, Training, Environmental and Quality issues.

Specialities: Change management, Program Management, People Management, Sales management,  Customer Relationship Management / Customer Satisfaction, Efficiency Improvements, Problem solving, Continuous Improvements.  Vast experience in global companies, specialised in the Nordic, UK, Scandinavian and Benelux market.
